The paper deals with location-based modeling and forecasting, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves spatial partitioning and time-series modeling, which are relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
